    <item>
      <title>日本西南部岛屿附近发生强烈地震</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/strong-earthquake-hits-near-japan-s-main-southwest-island</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据日本放送协会 (NHK) 报道，日本西南部九州主要岛屿宫崎县近海发生里氏 7.1 级强烈地震，并引发海啸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/strong-earthquake-hits-near-japan-s-main-southwest-island</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 08:21:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其排除提前降息的可能性，继续关注月度价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/turkish-central-bank-keeps-year-end-inflation-outlook-unchanged</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其央行表示，将维持货币政策紧缩，直至月度通胀率永久放缓，并强调其致力于避免过早降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/turkish-central-bank-keeps-year-end-inflation-outlook-unchanged</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 07:55:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
